room_title: Escape room "The Witchin’ Kitchen" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: Had such a great time. The Witchin' Kitchen Room was awesome! Definitely planning on going back! If you love puzzles you love Liberation Escape Rooms. Great fun!

room_title: Escape room "The Witchin’ Kitchen" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: Wicked good! Conquered the witch! Good fun and great staff!

room_title: Escape room "The Witchin’ Kitchen" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: We tried the Witchin' Kitchen tonight for my son's 12th birthday- it was awesome! The kids had an amazing time and the room was great!

room_title: Escape room "The Witchin’ Kitchen" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: I’m an escape room enthusiast and this establishment didn’t disappoint. The staff was amazing and the environment was very nice! We did Witches Kitchen and had a blast! It was challenging but not so difficult that we couldn’t escape. Our gamer was fantastic and I love that they get just as excited as the people who escape the rooms. Great time! Will definitely be back!
